Fig. 3A, B
). Gonocoel distinct, but not too deep; telopodites short, simple, biramous and distally carrying a long, in situ caudally directed and slightly bifurcate lamina with fringed/microspiculate lamellae; solenomere 
(sl)
slender and barely exposed; medial branch (
